vernac_cmds: Lemma eqRefl : forall (T : fol.System L) (a : fol.Term L), SysPrf T (equal a a).
replace (equal a a) with (substituteFormula L (equal (var 0) (var 0)) 0 a).
Lemma eqSym : forall (T : fol.System L) (a b : fol.Term L), SysPrf T (equal a b) -> SysPrf T (equal b a).
apply (impE L) with (equal a b); auto.
set (m := fun x : nat => match x with | O => a | S _ => b end) in *.
apply (impE L) with (subAllFormula L (impH (equal (var 0) (var 1)) (equal (var 1) (var 0))) (fun x : nat => match le_lt_dec 2 x with | left _ => var x | right _ => m x end)).
Lemma eqTrans : forall (T : fol.System L) (a b c : fol.Term L), SysPrf T (equal a b) -> SysPrf T (equal b c) -> SysPrf T (equal a c).
apply (impE L) with (equal b c); auto.
apply (impE L) with (equal a b); auto.
set (m := fun x : nat => match x with | O => a | S y => match y with | O => b | S _ => c end end) in *.

apply (impE L) with (subAllFormula L (impH (equal (var 0) (var 1)) (impH (equal (var 1) (var 2)) (equal (var 0) (var 2)))) (fun x : nat => match le_lt_dec 3 x with | left _ => var x | right _ => m x end)).

Fixpoint PairwiseEqual (T : fol.System L) (n : nat) {struct n} : fol.Terms L n -> fol.Terms L n -> Prop := match n return (fol.Terms L n -> fol.Terms L n -> Prop) with | O => fun ts ss : fol.Terms L 0 => True | S x => fun ts ss : fol.Terms L (S x) => let (a, b) := proj1_sig (consTerms L x ts) in let (c, d) := proj1_sig (consTerms L x ss) in SysPrf T (equal a c) /\ PairwiseEqual T x b d end.
Let termsMap (m : nat) (ts ss : fol.Terms L m) : nat -> fol.Term L.
exact (fun n : nat => match eq_nat_dec n (m + m) with | left _ => a | right _ => match eq_nat_dec n (S (m + m)) with | left _ => a0 | right _ => Hrecm b b0 n end end).
Remark subAllnVars1 : forall (a : nat) (ts ss : fol.Terms L a), ts = subAllTerms L _ (fst (nVars L a)) (termsMap a ts ss).
assert (forall v : nat, In v (freeVarTerms L _ (fst (nVars L a))) -> v < a + a).

replace (subAllTerms L a a2 (fun n : nat => match eq_nat_dec n (a + a) with | left _ => a0 | right _ => match eq_nat_dec n (S (a + a)) with | left _ => a1 | right _ => termsMap a b b0 n end end)) with (subAllTerms L a a2 (termsMap a b b0)).
Remark subAllnVars2 : forall (a : nat) (ts ss : fol.Terms L a), ss = subAllTerms L _ (snd (nVars L a)) (termsMap a ts ss).
assert (forall v : nat, In v (freeVarTerms L _ (snd (nVars L a))) -> v < a + a).

replace (subAllTerms L a b1 (fun n : nat => match eq_nat_dec n (a + a) with | left _ => a0 | right _ => match eq_nat_dec n (S (a + a)) with | left _ => a1 | right _ => termsMap a b b0 n end end)) with (subAllTerms L a b1 (termsMap a b b0)).

Remark addPairwiseEquals : forall (T : fol.System L) (n : nat) (ts ss : fol.Terms L n), PairwiseEqual T n ts ss -> forall m0 : nat -> fol.Term L, (forall q : nat, q < n + n -> m0 q = termsMap n ts ss q) -> forall f0 : fol.Formula L, SysPrf T (subAllFormula L (nat_rec (fun _ : nat => fol.Formula L) f0 (fun (n : nat) (Hrecn : fol.Formula L) => fol.impH L (fol.equal L (fol.var L (n + n)) (fol.var L (S (n + n)))) Hrecn) n) m0) -> SysPrf T (subAllFormula L f0 m0).
intros T n ts ss H.
set (m := termsMap n ts ss) in *.
apply (impE L) with (fol.equal L (m0 (n + n)) (m0 (S (n + n)))).
Lemma equalRelation : forall (T : fol.System L) (r : Relations L) (ts ss : fol.Terms L _), PairwiseEqual T _ ts ss -> SysPrf T (iffH (atomic r ts) (atomic r ss)).
set (n := arity L (inl (Functions L) r)) in *.
set (m := termsMap n ts ss) in *.

replace (iffH (atomic r (subAllTerms L n (fst (nVars L n)) m)) (atomic r (subAllTerms L n (snd (nVars L n)) m))) with (subAllFormula L (iffH (atomic r (fst (nVars L n))) (atomic r (snd (nVars L n)))) m); [ idtac | reflexivity ].
cut (SysPrf T (subAllFormula L (AxmEq4 L r) m)).

replace (prod_rec (fun _ : fol.Terms L n * fol.Terms L n => fol.Formula L) (fun a b : fol.Terms L n => fol.iffH L (fol.atomic L r a) (fol.atomic L r b)) (nVars L n)) with (iffH (atomic r (fst (nVars L n))) (atomic r (snd (nVars L n)))).
generalize (iffH (atomic r (fst (nVars L n))) (atomic r (snd (nVars L n)))).
replace (subAllFormula L (AxmEq4 L r) m) with (subAllFormula L (AxmEq4 L r) (fun x : nat => match le_lt_dec (n + n) x with | left _ => fol.var L x | right _ => m x end)).
clear m H ts ss T.
Lemma equalFunction : forall (T : fol.System L) (f : Functions L) (ts ss : fol.Terms L _), PairwiseEqual T _ ts ss -> SysPrf T (equal (apply f ts) (apply f ss)).
set (n := arity L (inr (Relations L) f)) in *.
set (m := termsMap n ts ss) in *.

replace (equal (apply f (subAllTerms L n (fst (nVars L n)) m)) (apply f (subAllTerms L n (snd (nVars L n)) m))) with (subAllFormula L (equal (apply f (fst (nVars L n))) (apply f (snd (nVars L n)))) m); [ idtac | reflexivity ].
cut (SysPrf T (subAllFormula L (AxmEq5 L f) m)).

replace (prod_rec (fun _ : fol.Terms L n * fol.Terms L n => fol.Formula L) (fun a b : fol.Terms L n => fol.equal L (fol.apply L f a) (fol.apply L f b)) (nVars L n)) with (equal (apply f (fst (nVars L n))) (apply f (snd (nVars L n)))).
generalize (equal (apply f (fst (nVars L n))) (apply f (snd (nVars L n)))).
replace (subAllFormula L (AxmEq5 L f) m) with (subAllFormula L (AxmEq5 L f) (fun x : nat => match le_lt_dec (n + n) x with | left _ => fol.var L x | right _ => m x end)).
clear m H ts ss T.
Lemma subWithEqualsTerm : forall (a b t : fol.Term L) (v : nat) (T : fol.System L), SysPrf T (equal a b) -> SysPrf T (equal (substituteTerm L t v a) (substituteTerm L t v b)).
elim t using Term_Terms_ind with (P0 := fun (n : nat) (ts : fol.Terms L n) => PairwiseEqual T _ (substituteTerms L _ ts v a) (substituteTerms L _ ts v b)); simpl in |- *; intros.
induction (consTerms L n (Tcons L n (substituteTerm L t0 v a) (substituteTerms L n t1 v a))).
induction (consTerms L n (Tcons L n (substituteTerm L t0 v b) (substituteTerms L n t1 v b))).

Lemma subWithEqualsTerms : forall (a b : fol.Term L) (n : nat) (ts : fol.Terms L n) (v : nat) (T : fol.System L), SysPrf T (equal a b) -> PairwiseEqual T _ (substituteTerms L _ ts v a) (substituteTerms L _ ts v b).
induction ts as [| n t ts Hrects]; simpl in |- *.
induction (consTerms L n (Tcons L n (substituteTerm L t v a) (substituteTerms L n ts v a))).
induction (consTerms L n (Tcons L n (substituteTerm L t v b) (substituteTerms L n ts v b))).
Lemma subWithEquals : forall (f : fol.Formula L) (v : nat) (a b : fol.Term L) (T : fol.System L), SysPrf T (equal a b) -> SysPrf T (impH (substituteFormula L f v a) (substituteFormula L f v b)).
apply eqTrans with (substituteTerm L t v a).
apply eqTrans with (substituteTerm L t0 v a).
apply impE with (substituteFormula L f1 v a).
apply impE with (substituteFormula L f0 v a).
apply impE with (substituteFormula L f0 v b).
decompose record (subFormulaForall2 L a v v0 a0).
decompose record (subFormulaForall2 L a v v0 b).
set (nv := v0 :: list_remove nat eq_nat_dec v (freeVarFormula L a) ++ freeVarTerm L a0 ++ freeVarTerm L b) in *.
apply (impTrans L) with (fol.forallH L (newVar nv) (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L (newVar nv))) v0 a0)).

assert (In (newVar nv) (freeVarFormula L (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x)) v0 a0))).
assert (In (newVar nv) (freeVarFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x)))).
apply (iffTrans L) with (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x)) x (var (newVar nv))) v0 a0).
apply (impTrans L) with (fol.forallH L (newVar nv) (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L (newVar nv))) v0 b)).
induction H7 as (x1, H7); induction H7 as (H7, H8).
induction H8 as [x1 H8| x1 H8]; [ induction H8 as [x1 H8| x1 H8] | induction H8 ].

apply (iffTrans L) with (fol.forallH L (newVar nv) (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x0)) v0 b) x0 (var (newVar nv)))).
assert (In (newVar nv) (freeVarFormula L (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x0)) v0 b))).
assert (In (newVar nv) (freeVarFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x0)))).
apply (iffTrans L) with (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L (substituteFormula L a v (fol.var L x0)) x0 (var (newVar nv))) v0 b).
